                <p class="text-body-sm md:text-body-md text-gray-800">
                    We use Monotree for three key aspects: internal communication, onboarding/training, and our
                    internal
                    social network. We aim to keep weekly content to ensure everyone stays connected and
                    informed, relying
                    mainly on news, courses, private and group chats, and bulletin boards. It helps us
                    tremendously with
                    operations, especially in keeping the entire team updated on operational changes,
                    promotions, and updates,
                    while also facilitating internal communication between teams. Monotree also aligns perfectly
                    with our
                    business strategy, which focuses on people. For us, communication and transparency are
                    essential, as is
                    keeping the entire team connected, regardless of how much we grow or how many cities
                    we&#039;re in,
                    preserving that family-like feeling. Monotree enables smooth communication across all teams,
                    ensuring they
                    stay informed and continue to build connections and experiences together.
                </p>
